between xApps and the RIC environment. It plays a critical role in optimizing **network automation, AI-driven xApps, and intelligent RAN control**. Integrating it properly enhances 
**5G network efficiency, reduces latency, and improves overall performance** in an open and programmable RAN architecture. ðŸš€
